    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this one go, but it\u2019s time for a new adventure! This beauty is in absolute mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one and it seriously looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and it drives like a total dream. You really have to see it in person to believe how clean it is! Shoot me a message if you want to come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
