      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in showroom condition and offering an unparalleled driving experience. This unit has been preserved to the highest standards, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in pristine, original state. For the discerning buyer seeking a vehicle of superior mechanical integrity and aesthetic perfection, this listing represents a rare acquisition opportunity. Every detail reflects meticulous care, ensuring this investment-grade example meets the most exacting requirements of automotive excellence.",
